{"type":"message","id":"8fd5c189","parentId":"dcb96c62","timestamp":"2026-03-23T10:42:52.500Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:9946cf88-21b8-426f-b7bf-d0ae030cf3b0 自我改进反思] 请执行自我改进反思（Self-Improving Agent）：\n\n1. 检查 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n2. 回顾最近主人的纠正\n3. 是否有重复模式需要固化？\n4. 是否有新的洞察需要记录？\n5. 更新 self-improving/memory.md\n\n记住：每次纠正都是成长的机会，不要浪费主人的每一次指导！\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 18:42 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-23 10:42 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774262572495}}
